      <body>
         <milestone n="792" unit="leaf" />
         <pb facs='#img_792'/>
         <metamark place="margin(top) margin(right)" function="folio" rend="no-caret _HMp" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0001" >199</metamark>
         <ab>
            <lb/>Preface.
            <lb/> ––––
            <lb/>"The sorrowful sighing of the prisoner" has
            <lb/>long come up 
            <lb/>
            <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _ink1" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0003" >^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0004" >into the ear of Him</add> <del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0002" >before the Lord</del>, who <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0025" >^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0005" >ever</add> "regards the
            prayer of the destitute":–– <subst facs="#img_792-0006" ><del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0006" >He</del><add place="inline" rend="no-caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1834a" facs="#img_792-0006" >The</add></subst> <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0026" >^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0007" >Lord</add> has heard their
            <lb/>voice, and looked on their affliction &amp; their labour
            <lb/>&amp; their oppression," &amp; "according to the greatness 
            <lb/>of his power", he hath 
            
            <metamark place="above" function="insertion-device" rend="insertion-device _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0008" >X</metamark> <add place="above" rend="insertion-device _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0011" >delivered them from their iron</add> <del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0009" >said unto the captives</del>
            <lb/><del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0010" >"Go forth".</del> <add place="above" rend="no-caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0012" >bondage.</add> "Not unto us O Lord, <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0014" >^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0015" >not unto us</add> but unto
            <lb/>thy name be <del rend="multi-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0013" >the</del> glory for thy mercy and thy
            <lb/>truth's sake."
            <lb/>
            <lb/>The storms which long have obscured the
            <lb/>face of the heavens are passing away––
            <lb/>brightening scenes &amp; fair prospects are opening
            <lb/>before us––the bow of promise is set in
            <lb/>the cloud––it is the memorial of mercy––
            <lb/>the pledge of peace.
            <lb/>
            <lb/>At such a period, the appearance of a
            <lb/>volume partly illustrative of the evils of
            <lb/>slavery <metamark place="inline" function="caret" rend="caret _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0016" >^</metamark><add place="above" rend="caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0017" >may</add> seem<del rend="hashmark _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0018" >s</del> seem to demand an explanation.
            <lb/>
            <lb/>The <del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0019" >fact</del> <add place="above" rend="no-caret _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0020" >truth</add> is, this little work was projected
            <lb/>more than seven years ago, when the state
            <lb/>of affairs, rendered it in the highest degree
            <lb/>desirable to engage by every legitimate effort
            <lb/>the thoughts &amp; feelings of the British nation on
            <lb/>this momentous question.
            <lb/>
            <lb/><del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0021" >The cause of the delay is</del> Circumstances
            <lb/>prevented the execution of the design––<del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0022" >The causes</del>
            <lb/><del rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#MAR" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0023" >of the delay are kn</del> To the Editors friend
            <lb/>––––––––––––––––
            <lb/><metamark place="margin(bottom)" function="composition-information" rend="insertion-device _ink1" change="St1833d" facs="#img_792-0024" >X ordained that the oppressed should go free.</metamark>
         </ab>
